{"tid":635017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒管強調，非常重視學生操守及學生宿舍的管理，對任何涉嫌違規行為都會嚴肅處理。","createTime":"2018-04-19T18:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T07:50:34.000Z","uid":5195,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"414dde75857d82e50499ac04d4a73f4e71e33209","tid":635017,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T18:36:42.000Z","msg":"沙田小瀝源恒生管理學院2名男學生涉藏毒被捕。恒生管理學院表示，就事件已經即時報警處理，警方將有關人士帶返警署協助調查。<br />\n警方指，上周四凌晨約2時，警方接獲恒生管理學院職員報案，指在懷疑學生在宿舍內吸食毒品。警員接報到場，在上址檢獲少量懷疑大麻草及懷疑毒品吸食工具。經調查後，2名分別21歲姓馬及22歲姓高男子，涉嫌管有危險藥物被捕。2名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於5月下旬向警方報到。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">恒管強調，非常重視學生操守及學生宿舍的管理，對於任何涉嫌違規行為都會嚴肅處理。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好熟口面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3535935925a3f0b5619ff537a84cfcb69d5a7ef2","tid":635017,"uid":139915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T18:43:50.000Z","msg":"恒大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5243edbf19805de419bd1780f15b9dd954f534d4","tid":635017,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67295f7b5210cb16f67f534cd420fb0809eab639","tid":635017,"uid":170733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99eb14ee3028689336e8975b71e1527a5a1f387","tid":635017,"uid":40779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"恒<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"